"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17645:\"<p>Looking for a Bluehost alternative to host your site? Bluehost is one of the most popular website hosting services on the market. It’s officially recommended by WordPress.org as well, adding to its well-earned reputation as a trusted web hosting provider.</p>\n<p>But, just because Bluehost is popular, doesn’t mean that it&#8217;s the right choice for your individual needs. In this article, we’ll show you the top 7 Bluehost alternatives so you can make an informed decision on the best hosting for your site.</p>\n<h3>Why Bluehost Alternatives?</h3>\n<p>While Bluehost is one of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/\">leading web hosting providers</a> that we often recommend, here&#8217;re a few reasons why some of our users want to try out a Bluehost alternative.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>No email-based support</strong>: In an effort to focus on providing instant support, Bluehost has discontinued email-based support. This can be frustrating when you want to fix advanced issues that may take a bit longer to resolve.</li>\n<li><strong>A monthly billing option isn’t available</strong>: When you subscribe to a Bluehost plan, you must choose at least a 12-month plan.</li>\n<li><strong>No website builder</strong>: Unlike most companies on the cheap hosting vertical, Bluehost doesn’t offer a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-website-builders-for-beginners-compared/\">website builder</a> with any of their plans.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Not interested in signing up for a Bluehost hosting plan? No worries!</p>\n<p>Below are a few different Bluehost alternatives that you might find more appealing. Before dive in, let’s take a look at our hosting review process.</p>\n<h3>About Our Top Bluehost Alternatives Review Process</h3>\n<p>We wrote this Bluehost alternatives review with a single goal in mind: help you easily choose the best Bluehost alternative for your website.</p>\n<p>Unlike other sites, we’ve actually signed up for some of the most popular hosting services on the market to evaluate their performance.</p>\n<p>Here’s exactly what we did:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Signed up with the top Bluehost alternative companies on the market</li>\n<li>Created a test WordPress site</li>\n<li>Installed a WordPress theme and added dummy content, including images, to mirror the actual live site environment on those test accounts</li>\n<li>Conducted a few different speed tests to see how the site would perform and recorded the test data</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Top 7 Best Bluehost Alternatives (2019)</h3>\n<p>Let’s get straight to the top Bluehost alternatives starting with #1 on our list.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/siteground-review.png\" alt=\"siteground review\" width=\"370\" height=\"227\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-221580\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/siteground-review.png 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/siteground-review-300x184.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. SiteGround</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 649 ms</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.98%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 10/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">SiteGround.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with SiteGround &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>Looking for a FAST Bluehost alternative? If speed is your top priority, then look no further than SiteGround. SiteGround is trusted by the owners of over 1 million domains.</p>\n<p>Unlike Bluehost, they offer 24/7 support via phone, live chat, and email-based tickets. You’ll also get free Cloudflare CDN, a website builder, and cPanel + SSH access with any of their plans.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Our users pay <del>$11.95</del> $3.95 per month (67% off)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/siteground-review/\">Read our SiteGround review &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hostgator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hostgator-review.png\" alt=\"hostgator review\" width=\"370\" height=\"220\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-221576\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hostgator-review.png 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hostgator-review-300x178.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hostgator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. HostGator</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 691 ms</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.96%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 10/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hostgator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">HostGator.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hostgator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with HostGator &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>HostGator provides you with more hosting options than Bluehost, such as shared hosting, cloud hosting, WordPress hosting, reseller hosting, etc. Their website builder lets you choose from over 100+ mobile-friendly templates.</p>\n<p>HostGator offers free transfers with all of their hosting plans within 30 days of signing up. They also offer AdWords and Bing credits to help grow your website along with 24/7 support via phone, chat, and tickets.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Our users pay <del>$6.95</del> $2.78 per month (60% off + free SSL)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/hostgator-review/\">Read our HostGator review &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/dreamhost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/dreamhost-review.png\" alt=\"dreamhost review\" width=\"370\" height=\"222\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-221574\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/dreamhost-review.png 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/dreamhost-review-300x180.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/dreamhost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Dreamhost</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 445 ms</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.90%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 7/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/dreamhost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dreamhost.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/dreamhost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with DreamHost &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>Just like Bluehost, DreamHost is also an officially recommended WordPress hosting service. They’re independently operated, unlike Bluehost, and have nearly 20 years of experience in web hosting.</p>\n<p>They provide you with a whopping 97-day money back guarantee, allowing you to try their hosting services risk-free. Best of all, with DreamHost, you can opt for a monthly plan if you’d like.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Our users pay only <del>$10.95</del> $2.59 per month (Free SSL + 76% off)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/dreamhost-review/\">Read our Dreamhost review &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ipage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/ipage-review.png\" alt=\"ipage review\" width=\"370\" height=\"217\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-221578\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/ipage-review.png 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/ipage-review-300x176.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ipage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. iPage</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 2.60 s</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.98%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 8/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ipage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">iPage.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ipage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with iPage &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>Do you think Bluehost is an overpriced hosting service? Then you might want to consider iPage.</p>\n<p>iPage is one of the cheapest (yet reliable) web hosting services on the market. With iPage, you can start a website for as low as $1.99 per month. They provide you with a basic drag and drop builder with limited features. They also offer $200 worth of free ad credits which Bluehost doesn’t.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Our users pay <del>$7.99</del> $1.99 per month (75% off + free domain name and SSL)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/ipage-review/\">Read our iPage review &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/greengeeks-review.png\" alt=\"greengeeks review\" width=\"370\" height=\"245\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-221575\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/greengeeks-review.png 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/greengeeks-review-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. GreenGeeks</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 697 ms</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.92%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 9/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">GreenGeeks.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with GreenGeeks &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>GreenGeeks is the world’s #1 eco-friendly web hosting provider. Unlike Bluehost and most other web hosting providers, GreenGeeks doesn’t upsell addon services with their hosting plans.</p>\n<p>GreenGeeks automatically updates your WordPress installs so you can have peace of mind knowing your website is secure. GreenGeeks offers US-based technical support via phone, live chat, and email/tickets.</p>\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Our users pay <del>$9.95</del> $2.95 per month (Free domain name + 70% off)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/greengeeks-review/\">Read our GreenGeeks review &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/inmotion-hosting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/inmotion-hosting-review.png\" alt=\"inmotion hosting review\" width=\"370\" height=\"202\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-221577\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/inmotion-hosting-review.png 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/inmotion-hosting-review-300x164.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/inmotion-hosting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. InMotion Hosting</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 982 ms</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.91%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 9/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/inmotion-hosting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">InMotionHosting.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/inmotion-hosting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with InMotion Hosting &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>InMotion Hosting comes with a lot of desirable hosting features such as a WordPress-optimized platform with server caching and SSD storage. They offer an unmatched 90-day money back guarantee to try out their service risk-free.</p>\n<p>Unlike other hosting providers, InMotion Hosting offers a WordPress-based page builder known as BoldGrid so you can quickly <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">build a flexible website</a> with WordPress via the drag and drop editor.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Our users pay only <del>$7.99</del> $4.99 per month (37% off + free domain name)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/inmotion-hosting-review/\">Read our InMotion Hosting review &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/a2hosting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/a2-hosting-review.png\" alt=\"a2 hosting review\" width=\"370\" height=\"206\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-221573\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/a2-hosting-review.png 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/a2-hosting-review-300x167.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/a2hosting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. A2 Hosting</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 1.28 s</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.90%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 9/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: A2hosting.com</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/a2hosting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with A2 Hosting &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>A2 Hosting is one of the best developer-friendly hosting services on the market. A2 Hosting lets you choose from 2 great operating system options: Linux and Windows. Their data centers are located around the globe in 3 different continents, so you can rest assured that your web pages are served quickly.</p>\n<p>Best of all, they provide you with an industry-leading anytime money back guarantee by which you can get a full refund for unused services at any time.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Our users pay only <del>$7.99</del> $3.92 per month (50% off)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/a2-hosting-review/\">Read our A2 Hosting review &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3>Recap: Top 7 Bluehost Alternatives</h3>\n\n<table id=\"tablepress-19\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-19\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1 odd\">\n	<th class=\"column-1\">WordPress Hosting</th><th class=\"column-2\">Cost</th><th class=\"column-3\">Money Back</th><th class=\"column-4\">Load Time</th><th class=\"column-5\">Uptime</th><th class=\"column-6\">Support</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-2 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>1. SiteGround</strong></a></td><td class=\"column-2\"><strong>$3.95/mo.</strong></td><td class=\"column-3\"><strong>30 days</strong></td><td class=\"column-4\"><strong>649 ms</strong></td><td class=\"column-5\"><strong>99.98%</strong></td><td class=\"column-6\"><strong>10/10</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hos